OL,3,CFailure to order Sean Brown public
OL,4,Cinquiry 'unlawful', court rules
OL,6,FMr Brown's widow Bridie Brown attended
OL,7,Fthe hearing at the Royal Courts of
OL,8,FJustice on Thursday.
OL,10,FDelivering the judgment on Thursday,
OL,11,Fthe Lady Chief Justice said: "We find
OL,12,Fthe decision to refuse a public
OL,13,Finquiry cannot stand and is unlawful
OL,14,Fand in breach of Article 2
OL,15,Fobligations."
