OL,6,FShe said she would adjourn the case
OL,7,Ffor four weeks to give the Secretary
OL,8,Fof State time to consider the judgment
OL,9,Fof the court and to confirm how he
OL,10,Fwould comply with the order.
OL,12,FShe said: "We stress there can be no
OL,13,Ffurther delay in this case."
OL,15,FLast year a coroner halted an inquest
OL,16,Finto the Brown killing, expressing
OL,17,Fconcern that his ability to examine
OL,18,Fthe case had been "compromised" by the
OL,19,Fextent of confidential state material
OL,20,Fbeing excluded from the proceedings on
OL,21,Fnational security grounds.
